title: [PS3] CFW 4.50 v1.00-FERROX
description: Here is a new Custom Firmware release for v4.50, following the previous releases from RazorX (PS3ultimate 4.50) & smhabib (Habib v4.50). This time around PS3 Developer Alexander known for his previous CFW releases and his Unofficial Fork of Iris Manager., has now released his latest CFW version. With his release of FERROX: 4.50 CFW v1.0, This CFW comes with alot of the usual patches and then some extras like the recent XMB Screenshot Patches that we reported recently and various other features you can see in the list from the Release
